# Build orchestrator
Tools/Build/config.local.json
Tools/Build/output/

# Vendored design system — installed via:
#   git submodule update --init Vendor/unity-ui-document-design-system
#   mklink /J Assets\DesignSystem Vendor\unity-ui-document-design-system\Assets\DesignSystem
# The junction is per-clone (Windows-only path; macOS/Linux contributors use ln -s),
# so we don't track the link itself OR Unity's auto-generated .meta for it.
Assets/DesignSystem
Assets/DesignSystem.meta

# Vendored sprite baker — same per-clone pattern as the design system:
#   git submodule update --init Vendor/unity-3d-to-sprite-baker
#   mklink /J Assets\SpriteBaker Vendor\unity-3d-to-sprite-baker\Assets\SpriteBaker
# Powers the 4 sprite destructibles in the demo (3D character → sprite atlas
# at start, then fracture the sprite quad into 2D pieces).
Assets/SpriteBaker
Assets/SpriteBaker.meta

